{"tid":1956062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［支持］傳推出 Shorts 短片服務   YouTube 與抖音正面競爭","createTime":"2020-04-03T02:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T03:05:47.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"536ddea128c3525ca7194df494e7e57c2c024203","tid":1956062,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"唐美鳳<br />\n大陸影音服務平台抖音（TikTok）在歐美等外國市場爆紅，Facebook 早前經已有所行動，推出全新短片服務 Lasso 與之競爭。短片平台 YouTube 亦不甘後人，有消息指他們會在短期內推出名為 Shorts 的短片平台，同樣以 TikTok 作為假想敵。<br />\n<br />\n根據外國傳媒取得的資料，Shorts 不會仿效 TikTok 以獨立程式的形式提供，而是整合到 YouTube 的 Android 或 iOS 手機程式內，但 YouTube 就會加入旗下 Music 服務的授權音樂內容，讓用戶可以編輯使用，令短片內容更豐富更時尚。報導指 YouTube 期望利用本身擁有的豐富影音內容素材，以 Shorts 吸引更多創作者加入。<br />\n<br />\n雖然 YouTube 現時每月活躍用戶超過 20 億，但 TikTok 在歐美等海外市場快速增長，吸引了很多使用者和創作者加入，對 YouTube 和 Facebook 都構成壓力，預期他們會更在短片服務平台更加著力，以避免用戶被 TikTok 吸走。<br />\n<br />\n來源：theverge<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/04/03/youtube-tiktok-competitor-shorts-music/hottopic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F04%2F03%2Fyoutube-tiktok-competitor-shorts-music%2Fhottopic%2F&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BoWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=936a28c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/04/03/youtube-tiktok-competitor-shorts-music/hottopic/</a>"},{"pid":"be57297a4a737b2a38c99f9fcf0b2c5748d233c3","tid":1956062,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:38:39.000Z","msg":"英文原source<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/1/21203451/youtube-tiktok-competitor-shorts-music-google-report\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2020%2F4%2F1%2F21203451%2Fyoutube-tiktok-competitor-shorts-music-google-report&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BoWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=d8c3d9a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/1/21203451/youtube-tiktok-competitor-shorts-music-google-report</a>"},{"pid":"fe0ec01b3b8292cd6316962e36aaeb422e88908b","tid":1956062,"uid":13767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"好事黎 唔想再睇豆陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67da8e383e9db65b7756aae16d8ea02b9f887d8","tid":1956062,"uid":150983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪又係奶共 兩件都係屎"},{"pid":"37139625314c21e68dcedac1ee23491700a46c2e","tid":1956062,"uid":101392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"但YouTube都好奶共...<br />\n要發展下本土短片平台"},{"pid":"dca0a1bc122c99167433be77e02bfebf0e7aa319","tid":1956062,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfa7a7658c8b6f90b3f158d84fcb6af02ece8b9","tid":1956062,"uid":115700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:51:31.000Z","msg":"無黃標先再講"},{"pid":"caec94ed217a79e92acfa3294fa9582b92f78369","tid":1956062,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:58:39.000Z","msg":"Tiktok頂到盡紅兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},{"pid":"e65a4da892325f6e1676e92ec174a6d9cd5b9a48","tid":1956062,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}